        <h1 class="text-center">About BibleBridge</h1>
        <p class="mt-4">At BibleBridge, we provide cutting-edge Bible software solutions designed for developers, churches, and ministries. Our software enables easy Bible integration with powerful features, seamless database connectivity, and a customizable user interface built with Bootstrap 5 and Smarty.</p>
